[1] Cholera - Haiti
Date: Mon 4 Apr 2011
Source: United States Agency for International Development (USAID)
[edited]
http://www.reliefweb.int/rw/rwb.nsf/db900sid/KKAA-8FM2VN/$File/full_report.pdf


As of 28 Mar 2011, cholera outbreak numbers at a glance:

Non-hospitalized cases: 270 997
Hospitalized cases: 144 768
Deaths due to cholera: 4766
Overall case fatality rate: 1.7 per cent

